  "short_description": "<div class=\"mod\" lang=\"en-IE\" data-md=\"61\">\n<div class=\"LGOjhe\" role=\"heading\" aria-level=\"3\" data-attrid=\"wa:/description\" data-hveid=\"CAwQAw\">\n<div>\n<p>This 60cm Freestanding Dishwasher in black comes with 7 programmes to choose from. The overflow protection and half load options are added benefits.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.nordmende.ie/images/logo/3yearGIBO.png\" alt=\"NordMende 3 Year Warranty\" align=\"right\" /></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Seven Programmes</li>\n<li>Twelve Place Settings</li>\n<li>Twelve Litre Water Consumption</li>\n<li>One &#8211; Nineteen Hour Start Delay</li>\n<li>Adjustable Top Basket</li>\n<li>Overflow &amp; Leakage Protection</li>\n<li>LED Display</li>\n<li>49 db(a) Maximum Noise Level</li>\n<li>A++ Energy Rating</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"d9FyLd\">*Register To Receive Your Free <b>3 Year Warranty</b></div>\n<p><span class=\"ILfuVd\"><span class=\"e24Kjd\">All <b>NordMende</b> household appliances are fully guaranteed for 2 <b>years</b> from the date of purchase. If you register online or with our customer service team within 30 days of purchase you will receive an additional 1 <b>year</b> free &#8211; so <b>3 years</b> in total.</span></span></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rc\" data-hveid=\"CAwQBA\" data-ved=\"2ahUKEwighILtvfDoAhUGShUIHTbNAlgQFSgCMAJ6BAgMEAQ\"></div>\n<div data-hveid=\"CAwQBA\" data-ved=\"2ahUKEwighILtvfDoAhUGShUIHTbNAlgQFSgCMAJ6BAgMEAQ\"><img class=\"size-medium wp-image-5550 aligncenter\" src=\"https://eddiemaguire.ie/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/3year-1-300x132.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"132\" /></div>\n",
  "description": "<ul>\n<li>Freestanding Dishwasher</li>\n<li>Black</li>\n<li>7 Programmes</li>\n<li>12 Place Settings</li>\n<li>12 Litre Water Consumption</li>\n<li>Adjustable Top Basket</li>\n<li>1-19 Hour Start Delay</li>\n<li>A+++ Energy Rating</li>\n</ul>\n<table id=\"product_comparison\" class=\"data-table compare-table\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th><span class=\"nobr\">Brand</span></th>\n<td>Nordmende</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th><span class=\"nobr\">Colour</span></th>\n<td>Black</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th><span class=\"nobr\">Fit Type</span></th>\n<td>Freestanding</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th><span class=\"nobr\">Dishwasher Type</span></th>\n<td>Standard</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th><span class=\"nobr\">No. of Place Settings</span></th>\n<td>12</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th><span class=\"nobr\">Adjustable Rack</span></th>\n<td>Yes</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th><span class=\"nobr\">Child Safety Lock</span></th>\n<td>No</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th><span class=\"nobr\">End of Cycle Indicator</span></th>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th><span class=\"nobr\">Delay Timer</span></th>\n<td>Yes</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th><span class=\"nobr\">Half Load Function</span></th>\n<td>Yes</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n",
